tips.text: Their signature rib is too tough.
Tea time set $18.80 for a waffle with honey butter and a scoop of gelato, and two drinks (any drink except the $8.90 ones). Waffle could be crispier.
Charcoal waffles goes well with Honey scotch and Salted Cameral. The only dumb and gimmicky idea that they have to it is to serve salted egg sauce that comes with it, but serve separately in a cup.
Sticky ribs are tasty but rather dry. Get the loaded tacos!
fried fish is really good. Very crispy. I like the chili too.
Kunefe is a must try and u will definitely come back for more!!
